Wednesday, December 22, 1999

MERIT DOCKET

99-1863. State ex rel. Walls v. Second Dist. Court of Appeals.

In Procedendo. On motion to dismiss. Motion to dismiss sustained. Cause dismissed.

Moyer, C.J., Douglas, Resnick, F.E. Sweeney, Pfeifer, Cook and Lundberg Stratton, JJ., concur.
